Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PartB
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身邊還有我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會和你並肩戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你分開後 我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何痛苦 我都想陪在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以回來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到你想保護的那個地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我們的加爾剛蒂亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想對我們的同伴出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！瞄準補正 東35 南58
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這精度太驚人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向加爾剛蒂亞申請發射實彈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮彈準備班從左舷調轉船體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二發準備即將完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意聽取發射命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到本應丟棄的破船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會飛上天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些船艙裡可是裝滿了炸藥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我輕點 輕點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東35 南58
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標坐標補正完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮彈裝填完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對衝擊干涉水幕 撒水開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…天梯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定到最大威脅對象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先進行排除
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測Striker已將目標更新為加爾剛蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫蓋爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫蓋爾大人會從根本上為我們消除威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的援軍來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 形勢會被扭轉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先攻下那座遺跡島
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要得到那些兵器…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 簡單來說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在能量被大炮吸走之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫蓋爾的手下可全都聚到下面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正符合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過一會兒 這座炮塔就會像氣球一樣炸裂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會蠢到讓這東西落到他們手裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這我行我素只懂耍帥的蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話 給我到展望台上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距到達加爾剛蒂亞還有318秒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也要截住它！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬆開！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂喂 那要怎麼辦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 加爾剛蒂亞的大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會把那座塔給轟飛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別開玩笑了 這可是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我數5下 你就跳下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5 4 3
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 1！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐！
